@page "/faq"
@page "/privacy"

<div class="faq-container">
    <h1 class="faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>What is Max Faceit Stats?</h2>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Max Faceit Stats is a comprehensive analytics tool designed to provide detailed insights into CS2
                player and team performance on the FACEIT platform.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Detailed player performance metrics and averages</li>
                <li>Team analysis and comparison tools</li>
                <li>Historical match data</li>
                <li>League statistics tracking</li>
                <li>Head-to-head player and team comparisons</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>How is this different from FACEIT.com statistics?</h2>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>While FACEIT.com provides basic statistics, this platform offers several advantages:</p>
            <div class="comparison-table">
                <div class="comparison-row header">
                    <div class="feature">Feature</div>
                    <div class="faceit">FACEIT.com</div>
                    <div class="tracker">Max Faceit Stats</div>
                </div>
                <div class="comparison-row">
                    <div class="feature">player Stats Overview</div>
                    <div class="faceit">Limited to individual stats</div>
                    <div class="tracker">search for any player<br>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="comparison-row">
                    <div class="feature">Team Stats</div>
                    <div class="faceit">minimal team statistics</div>
                    <div class="tracker">Detailed map statistics for any team</div>
                </div>
                <div class="comparison-row">
                    <div class="feature">Analysis Tools</div>
                    <div class="faceit">Limited to individual stats</div>
                    <div class="tracker">Advanced comparison tools for player and team analytics</div>
                </div>
                <div class="comparison-row">
                    <div class="feature">League Stats</div>
                    <div class="faceit">league statistics Limited to individuals</div>
                    <div class="tracker">Detailed season-by-season analysis for all ESEA players</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>Common Questions</h2>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Why can't i see detailed stats for every league season?</h3>
            <p>Detailed statistics are only available for matches played after June 16, 2024. This is when
                faceit started recording these extra statistics.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How often are statistics updated?</h3>
            <p>Statistics are updated in real-time as matches are completed on the FACEIT platform. When you search for
                a player or team, you'll always see their most current statistics.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can i see individual gun statistics?</h3>
            <p>Unfortunately faceit does not record kills for each gun. Only pistol and sniper kills. Whenever Faceit
                makes api updates, I will include any additional stats.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-section">
        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
        <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="privacy-section">
                <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
                <p>When using Max Faceit Stats, we collect:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Steam Profile URLs you search for</li>
                    <li>FACEIT profile information accessed through public APIs</li>
                    <li>Usage data through Google Analytics</li>
                    <li>Cookies and similar tracking technologies</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>How We Use Cookies</h3>
                <p>We use cookies to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Analyze site traffic and usage patterns</li>
                    <li>Remember your preferences</li>
                    <li>Improve your browsing experience</li>
                    <li>Track analytics data</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Third-Party Services</h3>
                <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Google Analytics for site usage tracking</li>
                    <li>FACEIT API for player statistics</li>
                    <li>Steam API for profile information</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Data Storage</h3>
                <p>We do not store any personal information. All player data is retrieved in real-time from FACEIT and
                    Steam APIs.</p>

                <h3>Your Rights</h3>
                <p>You have the right to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Opt-out of cookies (except essential ones)</li>
                    <li>Access publicly available information</li>
                    <li>Contact us about privacy concerns</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Contact</h3>
                <p>For privacy-related questions, you can reach us through:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Discord: pxnkcs</li>

                </ul>

                <p class="privacy-footer">Last Updated: @DateTime.UtcNow.ToString("MMMM dd, yyyy")</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .faq-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .faq-title {
        color: #fd7d27;
        font-size: 4rem;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        font-family: 'TolyerNo1', sans-serif;
    }

    .faq-section {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid #fd7d27;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;

    }

    .faq-section h2 {
        color: #fd7d27;
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-family: 'TolyerNo1', sans-serif;
    }

    .faq-answer {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .faq-answer ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding-left: 0;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .faq-answer ul li {
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
    }

    .faq-answer ul li:before {
        content: "•";
        color: #fd7d27;
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
    }

    .comparison-table {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(253, 125, 39, 0.3);
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .comparison-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 2fr;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(253, 125, 39, 0.3);
    }

    .comparison-row:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }

    .comparison-row.header {
        background-color: rgba(253, 125, 39, 0.2);
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .comparison-row>div {
        padding: 1rem;
        border-right: 1px solid rgba(253, 125, 39, 0.3);
    }

    .comparison-row>div:last-child {
        border-right: none;
    }

    .feature {
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .tracker {
        color: #90EE90;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .faceit {
        color: #fa7b7b;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .faq-item {
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .faq-item h3 {
        color: #fd7d27;
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-family: 'TolyerNo1', sans-serif;
    }

    .faq-item p {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @@media(max - width: 768px) {
            .faq-container {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            .faq-title {
                font-size: 2.8rem;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }

            .faq-section {
                padding: 1.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            }

            .faq-section h2 {
                font-size: 2.8rem;
                color: #fd7d27;
                font-family: 'TolyerNo1', sans-serif;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
                letter-spacing: 0.6px;
                border-bottom: 3px solid #fd7d2780;
                padding-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .faq-section h3 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
                color: #fd7d27;
                font-family: 'TolyerNo1', sans-serif;
                margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            }

            .faq-answer {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            .faq-answer h2 {
                font-size: 2.8rem;
                color: #fd7d27;
                font-family: 'TolyerNo1', sans-serif;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
                letter-spacing: 0.6px;
                border-bottom: 3px solid #fd7d2780;
                padding-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .comparison-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .comparison-row>div {
                border-right: none;
                border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(253, 125, 39, 0.3);
            }

            .comparison-row>div:last-child {
                border-bottom: none;
            }

            .comparison-row.header {
                display: none;
                /* Hide header on mobile for better space usage */
            }

            /* Add labels for mobile view */
            .feature::before {
                content: "Feature: ";
                color: #fd7d27;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            .faceit::before {
                content: "FACEIT.com: ";
                color: #fd7d27;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            .tracker::before {
                content: "Max Faceit Stats: ";
                color: #fd7d27;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

            .faq-item h3 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .faq-item p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
        }

        .privacy-section h3 {
            color: #fd7d27;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem 0;
            font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;
        }

        .privacy-section p,
        .privacy-section li {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.4;
            font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;
        }

        .privacy-section ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .privacy-section ul li {
            padding: 0.3rem 0;
            padding-left: 1.2rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .privacy-section ul li:before {
            content: "•";
            color: #fd7d27;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }

        .privacy-section a {
            color: #fd7d27;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .privacy-section a:hover {
            color: #ff8f44;
        }

        .privacy-footer {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            color: #8d8d8d;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>